  "descriptionShort": "Tourist trips refer to the number of trips made by individuals traveling abroad and staying overnight. A country with a ratio greater than one has more incoming than outgoing tourists (i.e. has more visitors than locals leaving).",
  "type": "float",
  "datasetName": "UN Tourism Statistics Database",
